### Hadith 2:226

*Narrated Um Salama:*

One night the Prophet got up and said, "Subhan Allah! How many
afflictions Allah has revealed tonight and how many treasures have been
sent down (disclosed). Go and wake the sleeping lady occupants of these
dwellings up (for prayers), perhaps a well-dressed in this world may be
naked in the Hereafter."

